taskParams.sql:
insert overwrite table bpd_db_sim.t2_strategy_effect partition(dt = '${date8}')
SELECT
	COALESCE(t1.strategy_id,0)
	,COALESCE(t2.group_id,0)
	,0
	,COALESCE(t2.page_id,0)
	,COALESCE(t2.channel,'')
	,COALESCE(t1.strategy_type,'')
	,COALESCE(t2.group_type,'')
	,COALESCE(case when t2.group_type = 'normal' then 'resource' else t2.group_type end,'')
	,COALESCE(case when t2.group_type = 'ab' then t1.group_name else t2.group_name end,'')
	,COALESCE(t1.position_id,'')
	,COALESCE(t4.exposure_num,0)
	,COALESCE(t4.exposure_cust_num,0)
	,CASE WHEN t4.click_num is not null then COALESCE(t4.click_num,0) else COALESCE(t5.click_num,0) end
	,CASE WHEN t4.click_cust_num is not null then COALESCE(t4.click_cust_num,0) else COALESCE(t5.click_cust_num,0) end
	,COALESCE(t1.resource_id,0)
	,0
	,0
	,0
	,0
	,0
	,0
	,'${date8}'
	,0
	,COALESCE(t2.operator_department,'')
	,''
	,''
	,COALESCE(t3.resource_name,'')
FROM
	(
select
	strategy_id,
	strategy_group_id,
	resource_id,
	position_id,
	strategy_type,
    group_name
from
	bpd_db_sim.t2_strategy
union all
select
	strategy_id,
	strategy_group_id,
	resource_id,
	position_id,
	strategy_type,
    group_name
from
	bpd_db_sim.t2_event_strategy
	) t1
left join bpd_db_sim.t2_strategy_group t2
on
	t1.strategy_group_id = t2.group_id
LEFT JOIN bpd_db_sim.t2_resource t3
on
	t1.resource_id = t3.resource_id
LEFT JOIN 
(
  	SELECT
		strategyid,
		dt,
		COUNT(DISTINCT customerid) exposure_cust_num,
		COUNT(DISTINCT adviceid) exposure_num,
		COUNT(distinct t1.usr_id) click_cust_num,
		COUNT(t1.usr_id) click_num 
	from
		bpd_db_sim.t2_exposure t 
	left join jx_poc.d_cust_event_info_4 t1
	on t.adviceid = t1.t_id 
	where dt = '${date8}'
	group by
		strategyid,dt
) t4
on
	t1.strategy_id = t4.strategyid
LEFT JOIN 
(
	select
		strategyid,
		dt,
		COUNT(DISTINCT usr_id) click_cust_num,
		COUNT(*) click_num
	from
		bpd_db_sim.t2_buried_point_new
	where
		`type` = 'hit_advert'
	and dt = '${date8}'
	group by
		strategyid,dt
) t5
on
	t1.strategy_id = t5.strategyid
insert overwrite table bpd_db_sim.t2_exposure select * from bpd_db_sim.t2_exposure where dt <> ${date8}
